GSM switches between registered and not registered in deep sleep mode.
The distributions have a fix for it so that the modem does not enter deep sleep mode
but with that you cannot reach maximum runtime.

A hardware fix for the deep sleep problem is described here.
[http://lists.openmoko.org/pipermail/hardware/2009-May/001192.html]

With that fix, you can enter deep sleep mode without the reregistering problem.

